{"tid":59143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逼智障女買貴金屬　實德經理判監1月","createTime":"2016-12-29T11:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T16:40:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98f48fb221895caa56d7f00c0e1cd28aa875f0b8","tid":59143,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">逼智障女買貴金屬　實德經理判監1月<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/liu_PhteB_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fliu_PhteB_1200x0.png&h=7dfd271a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實德環球金業（香港）的男客戶經理去年9月，於荃灣一快餐店強迫智障女子購買貴金屬，現場兩名食客見狀起疑，報警揭發事件。案件經審訊後，男客戶經理早前被裁定作出具威嚇性營銷行為罪名成立，今於西九龍裁判法院被判監1個月。<br />\n<br />\n海關不良營商手法調查組指揮官楊穎欣於庭外表示，歡迎法庭裁決，又指本案是《商品說明條例》修訂後，首宗就金融服務不良營商手法定罪的案件，亦答謝兩位作出舉報的市民出庭作證。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時指，被告廖永威（25歲）明知事主有智障問題，但仍用方法要她購買貴金屬，因有人報警，才可制止事情進一步發展，法庭須發出訊息，令犯案的人知道法庭有責任保護智力有問題的人。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告沒有案底，過往奉公守法，又指被告已遭還押兩星期，得到的教訓相當沉重，承諾以後會更循規蹈矩。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報／明報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/逼智障女買貴金屬-實德經理判監1月/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E9%80%BC%E6%99%BA%E9%9A%9C%E5%A5%B3%E8%B2%B7%E8%B2%B4%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC-%E5%AF%A6%E5%BE%B7%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A31%E6%9C%88%2F&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=184d84f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E9%80%BC%E6%99%BA%E9%9A%9C%E5%A5%B3%E8%B2%B7%E8%B2%B4%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC-%E5%AF%A6%E5%BE%B7%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A31%E6%9C%88%2F&h=b51462b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/逼智障女買貴金屬-實德經理判監1月/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161229/56105951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161229%2F56105951&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ebda2c45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161229%2F56105951&h=7faacc97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161229/56105951</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161229/s00001/1482998988609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161229%2Fs00001%2F1482998988609&d=2awl7aVtIIn4Kw4zsVcm1WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=69457678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161229%2Fs00001%2F1482998988609&h=81291dd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161229/s00001/1482998988609</a>"},{"pid":"9c838782be0fdcfa3ad084fd594310bec17c49f8","tid":59143,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少半年啦"},{"pid":"424d72b5b143dbfc3b533edd68a60260af0278fe","tid":59143,"uid":62377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"好撚憎呢種仆街，出唔返黎最好。"},{"pid":"db0c55c5a3a29c2544eb6496182d72fa6f6b1171","tid":59143,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"金融才俊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba0c75cb8ce8b4c4e971aa380b879f6983c5bdb","tid":59143,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"肯俾多少少唔霸住m記張凳咪冇事囉<br />\n<br />\nsuccess, empower your success <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f32dd9d0a4a99906b095425397dc59de750815","tid":59143,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2